  • Interface Summary

    PrivacyModeChooserFragment.ModeChangedListener

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomPrivacyModeFragment
    Created on 30.12.17 This Fragment provides a SettingsFragment used to customize the PrivacyMode.USER_DEFINED privacy mode.
    PrivacyModeAdapter
    Created on 08.03.18 This adapter takes PrivacyModes and displays them in a list.
    PrivacyModeChooserFragment
    Created on 21.02.18 This Fragment lets the user choose his preferred PrivacyMode.
    PrivacyModeView
    Created on 28.11.17 This View can be used to display the 'Privacy Mode/Score' of the user.
    PrivacyPreferenceActivity
    Created on 21.02.18 This Activity contains both the PrivacyModeChooserFragment and CustomPrivacyModeFragment which together make up the privacy settings.
